    {
      "_kind": "single_choice",
      "id": "q-475",
      "text": "**62  Hva skjer med trykket når luften har passert compressoren?**",
      "score": 1,
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "q-475-opt-1",
          "label": "True"
        },
        {
          "id": "q-475-opt-2",
          "label": "False"
        }
      ],
      "explanations": [
        "As air passes through a gas turbine engine, aerodynamic and energy requirements demand changes in the air's velocity and pressure. During compression, **a rise in the air pressure is required**, but not an increase in its velocity."
